1. Dropbox offers 2GB of storage for free, and up to 16GB for premium users;
2. It allows users to save and sync documents and files across all their devices; 
3. Its security features include encryption, two-step verification and password protection;
4. Dropbox allows for easy collaboration and collaboration with others;
5. It can open files from a variety of platforms and makes accessing them outside the office easier.
